Welcome to the repository for puppet manifests to manage Cloudera Hadoop distribution

Puppet is open source platform for system change and compliance management. Cloudera is company, which produced leading distribution for Hadoop ecosystem, which includes Hadoop common, HBase, zookeeper, oozie etc.

These manifests could be used to deploy and manage Cloudera hadoop distribution. Currently it know to deploy HDFS, M/R, Hbase, Zookeeper, Hive, Pig, Hue.

The package is available under Apache license.


Enjoy!
